comments: He makes learning about photography interesting.
Helped me make my pics better. Its planned out well for beginners photography class but more time with photoshop would help.
goes out of his way to help you but can be hard!

Took his Photo class, which sounded like fun. It WASN\'T! It\'s once a week for 5 hours long. He doesn\'t really teach you anything new. Rambles on and on and then gives you a lame project and expects you to figure it out on your own. Never once used the book, he made us buy. I took this class as an elective, I wish I hadn\'t!
